{"tid":1640221,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"《男兒當入樽》井上雄彥撐香港，follow蔡英文twitter，出征日本?","createTime":"2019-10-09T01:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T14:59:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":81,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"b95f99bb712ac651de3e275b090c7d53e90251c6","tid":1640221,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:30:37.000Z","msg":"會不會搞到中國政府禁日本漫畫來懲罰？<br />\r\n因為香港，又開多個日本戰場，打日本？<br />\r\n蝴蝶效應<br />\r\n<br />\r\n <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ayakijah/photos/a.204884716609379/781038602327318/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fayakijah%2Fphotos%2Fa.204884716609379%2F781038602327318%2F&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJwoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=9da06679\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ayakijah/photos/a.204884716609379/781038602327318/</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n蔡英文twitter<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/iingwen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fiingwen&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJwoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=97e77b99\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/iingwen</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n《男兒當入樽》井上雄彥<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/09/O49gWQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F09%2FO49gWQ.jpg&h=85a05d71&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n只是個雅奇讚好專頁<br />\r\n<br />\r\n【跟隨】<br />\r\n<br />\r\n大家知道灌籃高手的作者－－井上雄彥老師<br />\r\n他有追蹤小英的推特嗎？<br />\r\n沒錯，他居然有<br />\r\n大家知道他有按讚支持香港嗎？<br />\r\n沒錯，他是支持香港的<br />\r\n<br />\r\n嗚嗚，我真的好為自己能喜歡上這樣的老師為耀<br />\r\n我追隨的怎麼都是這麼棒的人呢？<br />\r\n但追蹤小英我是真的很意外啊，看來老師除了球壇外對時事也是有在關注的。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n想當然爾，中國的灌高粉應該很崩潰吧<br />\r\n不過相信他們對黨的赤誠是比櫻木的頭還紅還亮的<br />\r\n就不用替他們擔心了哈哈<br />\r\n<br />\r\n另外老師仍在連載中的REAL在前陣子復刊了喔<br />\r\n睽違多年，終於等到了啊嗚嗚嗚（別哭<br />\r\n<br />\r\n再一個另外，老師明年四月會推出新的灌籃高手畫冊喔喔<br />\r\n我真的要幸福死了，明年都給我好好投票<br />\r\n我才能放心的買回來享受啊！！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n井上老師，謝謝你，不但畫出了這麼棒的作品<br />\r\n也關心著我們，而不為錢所動。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n但老師本來就是這樣不畏威權的人呢，斷然在自己想要的地方完結還帶著版權出走集英<br />\r\n太、太帥了啦！！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n永遠令我敬重的創作者，井上雄彥。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/09/ZAuKNx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F09%2FZAuKNx.png&h=82955363&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24231d1ca039be763e21c33972b97e9323643085","tid":1640221,"uid":22675,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:31:17.000Z","msg":"柯南可能也要禁了，撐香港，為香港加油　<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://images.plurk.com/3D8T8mwIVOuwRs2d4WPt47.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.plurk.com%2F3D8T8mwIVOuwRs2d4WPt47.png&h=ab01d4a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d450a0dbf547881d52975db080a04cc473bdd40a","tid":1640221,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:31:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.plurk.com/p/niqqnl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.plurk.com%2Fp%2Fniqqnl&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJwoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=1fa58251\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.plurk.com/p/niqqnl</a>"},{"pid":"0397e56fb4a7215bc11a6c30b2a39898367d42fb","tid":1640221,"uid":40470,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:32:21.000Z","msg":"強国人又會衝出來話禁你個漫畫<br />\n<br />\n但其實你班撚樣由頭到尾都係偷圖來睇"},{"pid":"d77157ecf4b031a1991e80c31d6eddcc033cfedd","tid":1640221,"uid":191926,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:33:21.000Z","msg":"中國人：藍球呢種運動要徹底禁止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6d67b2af3f4996f72345b02af529836c7f0775","tid":1640221,"uid":318091,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:39:28.000Z","msg":"但其實強國人好似都係睇盜版，抵唔抵制都冇影響<br />\n<br />\n我仲記得銀魂完嗰陣，大陸人喊餐死話唔好完，俾人屌唔買正版淨睇盜版，銀魂冇錢賺咪摺埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1357db6ede98a766216383b20c743bb8035b0d81","tid":1640221,"uid":51840,"like":7,"dislike"